title: Lentil as Anything - Preston
typeOfFood: Vegan, International, Western, Buffet, Fast food, Australian
description: A cooperative without fixed prices and survives with a pay as you feel concept. Part of a social movement away from the global growth of economic rationalism toward a communal grassroots ethos. Offers lunch and dinner with one menu. Vegetarian turned vegan in 2015. Multiple locations. Accepts eftpos.
